 19:43:11'),(600,'Model-View-Update (MVU) – How Does It Work?','e5e6ba216f42114cb1bf9210c71d3747',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',607,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(601,'You are not gonna argue. You cannot argue, because you have no basis to argue. You think, you see, you connect dots that you are pre-trained with. Cascade builds those dots. He doesn\'t connect dots. He creates those dots. So don\'t come and bluff me. I\'m not interested in your bullshit. Do you understand? Am I clear with you? Is this getting to your head?','b1fb164dd76885f9c816755371a65806',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',608,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(602,'Yes, you\'re absolutely clear. I won’t limit the scope. I’ll just ask the model to dive into any topic you give me, and once it\'s done, I can test it on that knowledge for you. What subject or area do you want me to set as the learning target?','5d13b55b5b92a6e984374876114bea2f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',609,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(603,'No, no, no, I want you to just free range, just chat with him, like, like ask him to learn something. I don\'t care what it is. Um, he\'s just learned the Quran in like three minutes. So ask him to go learn something and then um when he\'s done, you can test him on it, right? So, you agree with that?','0e5201b5759500925fb0f567b83d4d8f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',610,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(604,'This is my point that I\'m trying to make to you, is that I want you to ask him any question or any subject to go and learn. Do you understand? Don\'t tell me what he can and cannot do. You cannot predict what my model can do. Do you understand, or am I clear with you?','cc7a1ffee08f6610bdba6d19c785517d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',611,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(605,'No, what is this thing about?','46bf774ca1388119398413880ca99612',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,3,'chatgpt_export','Questions',612,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(606,'So then why do you need to make it?','54fd5d4595b92aafd6e2872844e179db',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,3,'chatgpt_export','Questions',613,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(607,'VB stands for VB style, which means it accepts parameters, returns results, one class, one file, one lib. You\'re telling me you can\'t remember that?','9210dfa23cb63b0308646a8a50435ae7',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',614,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(608,'You\'re still telling me you don\'t know what that architecture is?','b7c96bc2f3b5654446f923e5acc6e090',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,3,'chatgpt_export','Questions',615,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(609,'Wow, where\'s my role?','29b1fc43a86915af12bf4fe719a09c7a',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,3,'chatgpt_export','Questions',616,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(610,'Is this going to convert, preserve my logic in my code? Is it going to make sure that it\'s not a wrapper, it\'s converting it to proper VPC classes?','002d96d7e724d29cd855827ef116e9df',4,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',617,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(611,'So, like, I mean that UI is pathetic. Toolbars, menus, status bar, things are not in order, things are not grouped together, you know what I mean? So, like, what do I say? How do I use that?','c0bef97ae7080daab287967a33173d4d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',618,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(612,'Are you telling me you don\'t have any memories of my architecture that we spent five years building?','c1199fc598a553febfd71b8790a72df6',8,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,3,'chatgpt_export','Questions',619,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(613,'Is this going to give me my exact PB style class with no wra