 it, do you understand?','84c9547115f18908282e7ccab8dc70e5',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1152,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1136,'So essentially, once it finds the table files, it can break the .db files down into table files and remove the .dbs once it\'s certain that the tables are all extracted. Then it can unify the table files. So that would make more sense, you know what I mean?','3ec59e0d5608f3cca5d7605bfb7a8f98',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1153,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1137,'In essence, I\\u2019m saying that backward logic is like building the solution from the finish line. You pick your end goal first, and then you ask, \\u201cWhat step comes right before that?','31b308d9f2c9f62650e3f3e0e400fda9',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1154,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1138,'So in the ZSH or ZSC, it must prevent what does it do?','0c79d49a5d123c4a528ddbcec9f6ce01',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1155,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1139,'It\'s just like a DOM in HTML, isn\'t it?','5d50441202bb4ba9cf442dae60da5f5c',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1156,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1140,'Nope, nope, nope, nope, nope. It\'s simple. All you have to do is detect the pattern of repeating patterns like user, AI, user, AI. That\'s all. It doesn\'t matter what the chat\'s about, you\'ll always find that same pattern, user, AI, you understand?','8effac04c9a3760d6c2e92c2ec5677da',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1157,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1141,'Okay, what I did was, uh, uh, what is the command?','c7f271be634d78890ca769e52dd2675f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',1158,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(1142,'So, how many, like, classes should it have, right? So, for exa