',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2494,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2476,'The bracket DOM in the central index is the source of truth\\r\\n# [ ] No, all changes must go through the central index\\r\\n# [ ] Yes, changes are preserved and merged during regeneration\\r\\n# [ ] Only certain sections are editable directly\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: How do we test a segment?','c3574bcb4cb1b935417b414376c01b30',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2495,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2477,'S] Use the run command to launch the segment with its UI and logic\\r\\n# [ ] Use built-in test framework with automated testing\\r\\n# [ ] Use external testing tools and frameworks\\r\\n# [ ] Manual testing through IDE integration\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What happens if we have conflicting changes?','323009f7f5c7f18c906475a1bfd68506',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2496,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2478,'S] The sync command will detect conflicts and provide resolution options\\r\\n# [ ] Last change wins automatically\\r\\n# [ ] Manual conflict resolution required\\r\\n# [ ] System prevents conflicting changes\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# ADVANCED FEATURES:\\r\\n# =================\\r\\n# Q: What is the reader-writer indexer?','e34bcb45890da0726000a4154a66d180',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2497,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2479,'S] Component providing bidirectional synchronization between central index and individual files\\r\\n# [ ] Simple file copying mechanism\\r\\n# [ ] Manual synchronization process\\r\\n# [ ] No synchronization needed - files are independent\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What is PyQt6 verification?','2b352f6160741dffc25a181fd3e0b769',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'ch