 Allow custom mapping registration in central YAML\\n# [ ] Allow plugin-based mapping discovery\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What is the default root widget class for a segment?','d1f0a704e55353083d5044fd30f08b04',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2575,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2557,'QWidget\\n# [ ] QDialog\\n# [ ] QMainWindow\\n# [ ] Determined by bracket root token (panel/dialog/window)\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What is the default layout policy if none is specified?','cd685f28204a517b60a8af953d70b43d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2576,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2558,'QVBoxLayout\\n# [ ] QHBoxLayout\\n# [ ] QGridLayout\\n# [ ] No layout; manual geometry only\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: How are layouts expressed in bracket_dom?','59d9fefad83f0599e8aebffaa474f915',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2577,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2559,'Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What are the default layout parameters?','08f4196f768c824a5d0852f58ce15e0c',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2578,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2560,'Must be explicit in brackets for determinism\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: How should size properties be represented?','02d6423dd053c73bc9eeb1f4c76ace07',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2579,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2561,'Policy rules\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What is the authoritative style system?','1e4f37b21e8631be3df88a69ffd9ac6c',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',2580,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(2562,'Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: How are colors represented?','a7d5bdced26a82fe929c4bb22727b8f4',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Qu