\'s Logic Rules\\n# SECTION_ORDER: -1\\n# ============================================================================\\n\\n# Q: What is the first thing Wayne does when starting any project?','818be8c3229d06063457a686bfe0454f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3668,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3649,'W] Define the exact final observable condition (destination)\\n# [ ] Collect requirements and tools\\n# [ ] Start coding immediately\\n# [ ] Research best practices first\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: How does Wayne approach problem-solving?','8022343aed6f708f7165da2d7eeecfc6',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3669,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3650,'W] Work backward from destination to present state\\n# [ ] Work forward from current capabilities\\n# [ ] Explore multiple approaches simultaneously\\n# [ ] Follow established patterns\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne consider \"prerequisites\"?','42566d78e417d8526b9a1250858337e7',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3670,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3651,'W] States that must exist immediately before destination is valid\\n# [ ] Things needed before starting\\n# [ ] Tools and frameworks\\n# [ ] Knowledge and skills\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: When does Wayne allow implementation to begin?','089289cdbd339d6e392d8aca962851c9',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3671,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3652,'W] Framework/methodology exists and is readable/transferable (another AI can follow it)\\n# [ ] Basic code structure is in place\\n# [ ] Development environment is set up\\n# [ ] Project folder exists\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Batteries exist\"?','1cf596e739226c40463d4417d841368e',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3672,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3653,'W] Required tools/components/artifacts exist as defined artifacts (not guesses)\\n# [ ] Libraries are installed\\n# [ ] Dependencies are available\\n# [ ] Code compiles\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Batteries charged\"?','841bb431b4e995b55542c6ba15b92726',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3673,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3654,'W] System runs end-to-end at least once producing destination output AND evidence is logged\\n# [ ] Code works in development\\n# [ ] Tests pass\\n# [ ] Basic functionality verified\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Batteries long-lasting\"?','5d5e61ee9483e418743f26dc941ec1a6',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3674,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3655,'W] Repeatability + stability across multiple runs (same inputs \\u2192 same outputs across 3+ runs)\\n# [ ] Code is maintainable\\n# [ ] Performance is acceptable\\n# [ ] Documentation exists\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Best batteries\"?','861d1475f8edbe116b1d775232b2c496',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3675,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3656,'W] Reusable + transferable to other models/operators (no hidden steps)\\n# [ ] Code follows best practices\\n# [ ] Architecture is clean\\n# [ ] Solution is elegant\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: If a gate fails, what does Wayne do?','3f6f8d562df501d3bdfc5612d44e070c',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3676,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3657,'W] Detect OS globally \\u2192 bind provider + optimize parameters for that OS (same structure, variable parameters)\\n# [ ] Write separate code for each OS\\n# [ ] Use cross-platform libraries only\\n# [ ] Target primary OS only\\n# [ ] Other: _____