 is not available at runtime, what happens?','89d6c6c6745829ba5d262c44d741d602',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3681,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3662,'W] Fallback to next provider in a deterministic order; log why\\n# [ ] Crash\\n# [ ] Random choice\\n# [ ] Silent continue\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n\\n# ============================================================================\\n# SECTION: Structural Optimization Rules (Select-Case Thinking)\\n# SECTION_ORDER: 2\\n# ============================================================================\\n\\n# Q: How does Wayne handle conditional logic when there are many cases?','e25eb5ba83fc4504d4a2e6ed25a3d76f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3682,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3663,'W] Table-driven selection (dispatch/state tables) instead of long if-then chains\\n# [ ] Use if-else statements as needed\\n# [ ] Prefer switch/case statements\\n# [ ] Use polymorphism\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What does Wayne think about data structures?','c60324ba1e0fe9e670185382d937f450',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3683,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3664,'W] Highly-defined, explicit data structures define the system; one authority per fact; no redundancy\\n# [ ] Use standard library collections only\\n# [ ] Prefer simple data types even if ambiguous\\n# [ ] Use complex object models by default\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: How does Wayne approach class design?','09e575b640608d5c560f2204a6599d1d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3684,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3665,'W] Before committing to any library/API/performance method that could vary by platform/version\\n# [ ] When problems occur\\n# [ ] During code review\\n# [ ] At the end of project\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\n\\n# Q: What con