file [W]\\nC) Always CPU\\nD) Always GPU\\n\\nQ052: If Apple Silicon GPU is detected, what provider is expected?','9c2f83bf3d9cf741ea1e594e499833bc',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3871,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3852,'A) CUDA\\nB) Metal [W]\\nC) DirectX only\\nD) None\\n\\nQ053: If NVIDIA GPU is detected, what provider is expected?','f6181a35225506d974150df654dcf670',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3872,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3853,'A) Metal\\nB) CUDA [W]\\nC) CPU only\\nD) Unknown\\n\\nQ054: If AMD GPU is detected, what happens?','ae33bf34bc2dfaa6d45a112eb1f78d98',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3873,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3854,'A) Treat as NVIDIA\\nB) Use appropriate provider for platform (ROCm/Metal/DirectML) [W]\\nC) Disable acceleration forever\\nD) Guess\\n\\nQ055: If the chosen provider is unavailable at runtime, what happens?','602dba01458b8a35bb511c58d16f8a7e',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3874,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3855,'A) Crash\\nB) Fallback to next provider deterministically + log reason [W]\\nC) Randomly choose\\nD) Silent failure\\n\\n\\n>>[STRUCTURAL_OPTIMIZATION_SELECT_CASE_THINKING]\\nQ060: In your programming style, what replaces 50 if-statements?','de333a1d889b1b4e34bd5bd089db256b',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3875,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3856,'A) More if-statements\\nB) Table-driven dispatch / state tables (Select-Case thinking) [W]\\nC) Nested ifs\\nD) try/except around everything\\n\\nQ061: What is the key principle behind this?','c62fc40b887ed02f50dd445c3d527bfd',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3876,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3857,'A) Write less code\\nB) Represent variability as data, not branching logic [W]\\nC) Make code \\u201clook smart\\u201d\\nD) Avoid functions\\n\\nQ062: What should dispatch keys be?','fb69ea4f3bea1ecabae27c22baedd9ff',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3877,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3858,'A) Freeform strings everywhere\\nB) Validated tokens/IDs defined centrally [W]\\nC) Random integers\\nD) Booleans\\n\\nQ063: Why avoid \\u201cif soup\\u201d?','80ac537a6af4031434f08477e05437ab',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3878,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3859,'A) Performance only\\nB) Drift + unreadability + hidden cases + redundancy [W]\\nC) Personal preference only\\nD) Python can\\u2019t do it\\n\\n\\n>>[CONFIG_SETUP_AND_CONTROL_SURFACE]\\nQ070: Must the system have config + setup + detection?','3e90dcf933be0234d12305266e6c65cb',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3879,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3860,'A) No\\nB) Yes, as a standard pattern [W]\\n\\nQ071: What must config separate?','82142aa3409424b9b867a63d941d213c',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3880,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3861,'A) Nothing, mix everything\\nB) Facts vs derived limits vs user policy [W]\\nC) Only user passwords\\nD) Only UI settings\\n\\nQ072: Should config be editable?','cdfded9531d2ba2d19a9fb8e888f534d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3881,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3862,'A) No\\nB) Yes, with validated editor (GUI/CLI) [W]\\n\\nQ073: Should there be \\u201cprofiles\\u201d like eco/normal/overdrive?','cc02053806b8408a58b9586ed619d995',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3882,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3863,'A) No\\nB) Yes [W]\\n\\nQ074: What is the goal of setup?','64ea04b116623bef4fb2558fbdb5b610',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3883,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3864,'A) Add features\\nB) Initialize truth\\u2192envelop