-07-02 19:43:11'),(3870,'A) Keep building anyway\\nB) Stop expansion; diagnose; tighten parameters; retest [W]\\nC) Ignore it\\nD) Increase overdrive\\n\\n\\n>>[TRANSFERABILITY_AND_DONE]\\nQ100: Is the system done if only Wayne can reproduce it?','6c2a49a61e7bcdf26d1cf94f9fedf3c1',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3890,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3871,'A) Yes\\nB) No [W]\\n\\nQ101: What is the finish condition?','84b079aaadefd984489d25f656eec2bc',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3891,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3872,'A) Code compiles\\nB) Destination achieved once\\nC) Destination achieved + repeatable + env-optimized + transferable (no hidden steps) [W]\\nD) Documentation is long\\n\\nQ102: What does \\u201cmasterpiece\\u201d mean in this protocol?','391c35d7fe6e207dcd02ef8c775ce109',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3892,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3873,'And then the code, I don\'t know if it\'s going to need two different parts or what, you know what I mean?','665e76f7e75432a549c49567ffc4f2f2',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3893,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3874,'HARD_MAX_REPLY_BYTES),\\n                json ?','d100412aee6d4ba806dbc17187c1f9ce',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3894,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3875,'HARD_MAX_REPLY_BYTES) break;\\n    off += snprintf(buf + off, HARD_MAX_REPLY_BYTES - off,\\n                    \"%s\\\\\"%s\\\\\"\",\\n                    first ?','b2f6fff6a544808d26f557f659ecffe7',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3895,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3876,'Mongoose_an_embeddable_web_server_in_C?','3bd1c5ee09456eda47fe3b09d46f4188',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3896,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3877,'Read more\",                     \