least once with evidence\\r\\n# [ ] Code works in development\\r\\n# [ ] Tests pass\\r\\n# [ ] Basic functionality verified\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Batteries long-lasting\"?','c85820dd1446d490a5f95c6e13bec07d',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3947,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3928,'A] Repeatability + stability across multiple runs\\r\\n# [ ] Code is maintainable\\r\\n# [ ] Performance is acceptable\\r\\n# [ ] Documentation exists\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne mean by \"Best batteries\"?','0e00d809531c51a3d8a3f81ef3bb2a14',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3948,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3929,'A] Detect OS \\u2192 switch to OS-specific optimization strategy\\r\\n# [ ] Write separate code for each OS\\r\\n# [ ] Use cross-platform libraries only\\r\\n# [ ] Target primary OS only\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne do about system resources (RAM, GPU, CPU)?','80cb10be5b5b8d88af96dc1a59c24758',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3949,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3930,'A] Detect resources \\u2192 compute safe envelope \\u2192 adapt parameters\\r\\n# [ ] Assume minimum requirements\\r\\n# [ ] Require high-end hardware\\r\\n# [ ] Ignore resource constraints\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: How does Wayne handle user performance preferences?','94c54c0ea92fb1838ef61465fedc48d4',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3950,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3931,'A] Allow manual override modes within hard safety caps\\r\\n# [ ] Use fixed performance settings\\r\\n# [ ] Let users configure anything\\r\\n# [ ] Ignore user preferences\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What is Wayne\'s approach to code optimization?','32360c4140204bd720cb839d1efbbc31',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3951,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3932,'A] Table-driven selection instead of long if-then chains\\r\\n# [ ] Use if-else statements as needed\\r\\n# [ ] Prefer switch/case statements\\r\\n# [ ] Use polymorphism\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne think about data structures?','9b7d3d409f20a92b40ce6c9d7e10cff1',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3952,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3933,'A] Highly-defined, explicit data structures define the system\\r\\n# [ ] Use standard library collections\\r\\n# [ ] Prefer simple data types\\r\\n# [ ] Use complex object models\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: How does Wayne approach class design?','6682db5d4395bfb990775c0e5074a742',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3953,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3934,'A] Before committing to any library/API/performance method\\r\\n# [ ] When problems occur\\r\\n# [ ] During code review\\r\\n# [ ] At the end of project\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What constitutes \"evidence\" for Wayne?','11bcd995c6a41bf2ba814593e495cb3f',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3954,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3935,'A] Measured proof (run results) + repeatability validation\\r\\n# [ ] Unit tests passing\\r\\n# [ ] Code compiles without errors\\r\\n# [ ] Manual testing\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: How does Wayne validate \"optimized\" claims?','95963c6c2bec42108efb59d99af877fb',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3955,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3936,'A] Same inputs produce same outputs across 3+ runs\\r\\n# [ ] Performance benchmarks\\r\\n# [ ] Code review\\r\\n# [ ] User acceptance\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# ============================================================================\\r\\n# WAYNE\'S MODE SELECTION LOGIC\\r\\n# ============================================================================\\r\\n\\r\\n# SECTION: Decision Modes\\r\\n# SECTION_ORDER: 4\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: When does Wayne use \"Wayne mode\"?','47d13e20ea8069c588ced5d67692f1f2',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3956,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3937,'A] Core/infrastructure systems OR repeated failures OR multi-machine\\r\\n# [ ] All projects\\r\\n# [ ] Complex problems only\\r\\n# [ ] When time permits\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: When does Wayne use \"Practical mode\"?','52b174a862d25b9fd5ce76d1caeb59ee',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3957,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3938,'A] Default mode; complete DataFlow + Test_Plan, build minimal slice\\r\\n# [ ] Simple projects\\r\\n# [ ] Prototyping\\r\\n# [ ] Learning projects\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: When does Wayne use \"Minimal mode\"?','5ebb6758c737f6a7d509b4f3a390b362',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3958,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3939,'A] Throwaway experiments only (never for core systems)\\r\\n# [ ] Quick prototypes\\r\\n# [ ] Learning exercises\\r\\n# [ ] Small utilities\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What never gets deescalated from Wayne mode?','243ed814bb330be42b81344e69fb2537',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3959,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3940,'A] Security/authentication/remote access components\\r\\n# [ ] User interface code\\r\\n# [ ] Performance-critical sections\\r\\n# [ ] Documentation\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# ============================================================================\\r\\n# WAYNE\'S FINISH CONDITIONS\\r\\n# ============================================================================\\r\\n\\r\\n# SECTION: Completion Criteria\\r\\n# SECTION_ORDER: 5\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What is Wayne\'s definition of \"done\"?','3fca904b5e369f0c0be1b40bc695ff9e',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3960,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3941,'A] Destination capability achieved + repeatable + environment-optimized + verified best-known approach\\r\\n# [ ] All features implemented\\r\\n# [ ] Tests passing\\r\\n# [ ] Documentation complete\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne require before calling something \"charged\"?','cd6797c5b78b30171ea03078184ed587',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3961,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3942,'A] Dry run executed + evidence report created + repeatable outcomes\\r\\n# [ ] Basic functionality works\\r\\n# [ ] Code is tested\\r\\n# [ ] Performance is acceptable\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What does Wayne require before calling something \"best\"?','0c5c88bed11c52276a6c6afcdf1d9af9',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,1,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3962,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11'),(3943,'A] Complete preparation before implementation\\r\\n# [ ] Always write tests\\r\\n# [ ] Document everything\\r\\n# [ ] Use version control\\r\\n# [ ] Other: _________________________\\r\\n\\r\\n# Q: What is Wayne\'s non-negotiable rule about online verification?','4d7d9c1a21b76eeaf4b88fc077254ba9',9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'chatgpt','',0,1,2,'chatgpt_export','Questions',3963,'question_text','2026-07-02 19:43:11');

